            "content_html": "<p>Link notebook: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cua2FnZ2xlLmNvbS9jb2RlL2hhb3RpZW5kdWNhbmgvZG5uLWNubi1iZXJ0\">DNN-CNN-BERT</span></p>\n<p>Note: I use tiny-bert model <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/gaunernst/bert-tiny-uncased\"> <code>gaunernst/bert-tiny-uncased</code> </a> to minimize computational resources</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#contents\">#</a> Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#Overview\">Overview</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Two-label-multimodal\">Two-label multimodal classification report</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#Five-label-multimodal\">Five-label multimodal classification report</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"overview\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#overview\">#</a> Overview</h2>\n<p><strong>Two-label multimodal</strong><br />\n<img data-src=\"/assets/multimodal-android-malware-detection/multimodal-android-malware-detection-20240901-01.png\" alt=\"cfm\" /><br />\n<img data-src=\"/assets/multimodal-android-malware-detection/multimodal-android-malware-detection-20240901-02.png\" alt=\"acc_compare\" /><br />\n<img data-src=\"/assets/multimodal-android-malware-detection/multimodal-android-malware-detection-20240901-03.png\" alt=\"loss_compare\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Five-label multimodal</strong></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/multimodal-android-malware-detection/multimodal-android-malware-detection-20240901-04.png\" alt=\"cfm\" /><br />\n<img data-src=\"/assets/multimodal-android-malware-detection/multimodal-android-malware-detection-20240901-05.png\" alt=\"acc_compare\" /><br />\n<img data-src=\"/assets/multimodal-android-malware-detection/multimodal-android-malware-detection-20240901-06.png\" alt=\"loss_compare\" /></p>\n<h2 id=\"two-label-multimodal\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#two-label-multimodal\">#</a> Two-label multimodal</h2>\n<p>Self-attention</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><s